				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">This article is an accessible, non-technical introduction to the subject. For the main encyclopedia article, see <a href="Quantum_mechanics" title="Quantum mechanics">Quantum mechanics</a>.</div>
<table class="vertical-navbox nowraplinks" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="float:right;clear:right;width:22.0em;margin:0 0 1.0em 1.0em;background:#f9f9f9;border:1px solid #aaa;padding:0.2em;border-spacing:0.4em 0;text-align:center;line-height:1.4em;font-size:88%;width:18.5em;">
<tr>
<th class="" style=";padding:0.2em 0.4em 0.2em;;font-size:145%;line-height:1.2em;"><a href="Quantum_mechanics" title="Quantum mechanics">Quantum mechanics</a></th>
